latestPosts.caption:
I click pictures not just to post, but to remember. To freeze moments that feel like home, to hold onto the way light touched my face, or how I laughed when no one was watching. It’s not about perfection—it’s about preservation. Nostalgia has become softer now, something I welcome with open arms. No more pain, no more revenge. Just love for the life I’ve lived and the memories I’m still making. This is the happiest I’ve ever been, and I want to remember every second of it.

#nostalgia
